<item>
            <title>[LU-1450] parallel-scale produces malformed results.yml file</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1450</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Parallel-scale sometimes produces malformed results.yml files when running on autoetst. An example is &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d3b1917a-aa27-11e1-bd84-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d3b1917a-aa27-11e1-bd84-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; .It has 7 subtests msarked as pass, and then the beginning of an eighth test (test_iorfpp) which has nothing other than a name. Maloo presently just shows the passed tests but marks the whole test suite as FAIL.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="14624">LU-1450</key>
            <summary>parallel-scale produces malformed results.yml file</summary>
